-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
New in 0.2.0

* New embedded AI Engine : FAILE by Adrien Regimbald  (up to 2250 ELO)
* Chess rules now totaly respected (even little details)
* An option menu with a completely new GUI (sxmlGUI)
* A lot of new options
* Save configuration file in user's home directory (Linux only)
* The decor is now a skybox
* Multi-languages supported
* Source code is now completely in english
* Use Scons build system for build and install
* A lot of other little improvements


